WEBVTT

00:00.320 --> 00:01.160
In reply to Father

00:01.520 --> 00:02.440
The order was given by your son

00:03.600 --> 00:04.880
Chu Huan only followed orders

00:05.160 --> 00:06.640
What do you mean you gave the order?

00:06.960 --> 00:07.880
I tell you

00:08.040 --> 00:09.160
This is Chu Huan

00:09.160 --> 00:10.280
Giving his own order

00:10.360 --> 00:11.360
He wanted to rebel

00:11.400 --> 00:12.360
Do you understand?

00:12.560 --> 00:13.640
But that's not how it was

00:14.040 --> 00:14.760
I beg Father

00:14.960 --> 00:15.600
To spare his life

00:15.800 --> 00:16.360
He was also
